## Technical Implementation

### Authentication & Authorization
- Uses `requireAuthWithClient()` for user authentication
- Uses `requireAdmin()` for admin-only routes
- Supports both cookie-based and Bearer token authentication
- Proper error handling with 401/403 status codes

### Validation
- Zod schemas for request body validation
- Query parameter validation with type coercion
- UUID format validation
- Enum validation for XP sources
- Positive integer validation for amounts

### Error Handling
- Centralized error handling with `handleApiError()`
- Proper HTTP status codes
- Descriptive error messages
- Validation error details

### Integration
- Uses XPService for all XP operations
- Leverages Supabase client for database access
- Follows existing codebase patterns and conventions
- Compatible with existing middleware and utilities

